Wrapping up #Cyberpunk2077 this week. After experiencing several endings over the weekend, I have my one actual major disappointment. All major job (main quests) dialog parts should have been in 3rd person camera view. Would have been much more cinematic and hard hitting.

Maybe with a bit more patience she would have come to a better place, or maybe she had something organic to deal with and the mods were just an external bandaid. What we cover up can come home to roost in the most abrupt inevitability. #cyberpunk2077
